summary: Enthusiastic,sportive, goal oriented and humble. I find it rewarding to engage with patients with complex needs and persistent pain. With a holistic approach, I focus on the incremental improvement of physical, cognitive and psychological factors that impedes a comfort and happy lifestyle. Our comfort and happiness unconsciously relinquishes the beauty of life engrave in our hearts. This is what I strive for.
